This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language semantics and quantifiers. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as these fields often deal with natural language processing and semantics. Additionally, the use of bialgebras suggests a connection to algebraic structures, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
